		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_INDIA_UE_CHOICE_4_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_INDIA_UE_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} has his Engineers re-sculpt the various Castles in his Cities.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_INDIA_UE_CHOICE_5_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_INDIA_UE_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} begins a new Era of political thought!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_INDIA_UE_CHOICE_6_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_INDIA_UE_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} personally leads a non-violent campaign for social improvement in India!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Heart Without Words</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_HELP">
			<Text>Peace follow you throughout all your doings, Mahatma. If it is not to much bother, your wisdom is requested in council. We need it much of late.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Receive a Great Person of your choice.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Monuments of the conquest generate +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith, and increase [ICON_FOOD] Growth by 10%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Allow the priests {2_InstantYield}. A Mandir is constructed in every City. All Mandirs these generate +1 [ICON_FOOD] Food and +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Permit plans worth {2_InstantYield} to be enacted. All Castles generate +2 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture, [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism, and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Conscript {2_InstantYield} in every City into a Fusilier. Enter a [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age for {4_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>Use {2_InstantYield} to call upon {4_Turns} of Resistance. Unhappiness thresholds of [ICON_GOLD] Poverty, [ICON_RESEARCH] Illiteracy, and [ICON_RELIGION] Religious Divisions are reduced by 25%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*A recent birth has been identified as the reincarnation of a Great Person*[NEWLINE]A Great Soul is returned to us! Make the necessary arrangements.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*The conquest of foreign lands still breeds contempt among old enemies*[NEWLINE]We must start a campaign for truth and forgiveness! Let us remember that we are more similar than we are different, that we might learn to love one another again.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*The priest of the Grand Temple malign the state of worship in India. They wish to see great spires erected for the glory of heaven!*[NEWLINE]We must do whatever we can to lead men towards heaven. Let it be.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*Our Engineers believe that with new technologies, many of the old fortifications which are falling into disuse can be renovated in the new style*[NEWLINE]To see these bastions of war transformed into palaces of holiness and protection brings great joy to my soul.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>*Our Military Advisor has penned a text dubbed Adnyapatra, he would have us impliment its suggestions*[NEWLINE]It pains me to see a drop of blood spilt in my name, but if I cannot convince men to accept peace, I must force it on them.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_INDIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>*The people are increasingly resentful of the roles imposed upon them by outdated social expectations*[NEWLINE]As the Empire has grown further from its roots, so too have we grown further from the Truth. It now falls to me to lead us back...</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
</GameData>